title: USWNT drops from top spot in FIFA rankings for first time since 2015
text:
Mar 24, 2017 at 1:09p ET 0Shares Â© Yellow Card Journalism, LLC., Icon Sports Media, Inc. (Icon SMI) --ALL RIGHTS RESERVED-- Icon Sportswire via Getty Images 
A rough showing at the SheBelieves Cup, where the USWNT finished last in the round-robin tournament, saw the U.S. slip in the latest FIFA rankings. The USWNT had held the top spot since reclaiming it in July 2015.
